					<description><![CDATA[羽毛球名将谢儮好（CHEAH Liek Hou）今天下午（9月4日）在SU5级（上肢残障）决赛，直落两局力挫印尼“死敌”德瓦（Dheva Anrimusthi），为大马代表团赢得本届东京残奥会第二金！]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p></p>



<div class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow aligncenter" data-effect="slide"><div class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_container swiper-container"><ul class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_swiper-wrapper swiper-wrapper"><li class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide"><figure><img loading="lazy" width="800" height="532" alt="" class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-24526" data-id="24526" src="https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/40fed0e9-4703-4965-87f7-bf242227588f.jpg?x-oss-process=style/imgcompress" srcset="https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/40fed0e9-4703-4965-87f7-bf242227588f.jpg?x-oss-process=style/imgcompress 800w, https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/40fed0e9-4703-4965-87f7-bf242227588f-300x200.jpg 300w, https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/40fed0e9-4703-4965-87f7-bf242227588f-768x511.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><figcaption class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption">确定胜利后，謝儮好躺在地上呐喊，久久不能自已。 （图：大马国家体育理事会面子书）</figcaption></figure></li><li class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide"><figure><img loading="lazy" width="800" height="532" alt="" class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-24527" data-id="24527" src="https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/9494641c-73f4-4094-be00-03765a8b5ad8.jpg?x-oss-process=style/imgcompress" srcset="https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/9494641c-73f4-4094-be00-03765a8b5ad8.jpg?x-oss-process=style/imgcompress 800w, https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/9494641c-73f4-4094-be00-03765a8b5ad8-300x200.jpg 300w, https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/9494641c-73f4-4094-be00-03765a8b5ad8-768x511.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><figcaption class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption">謝儮好（右）赛后感谢恩师、大马羽球名宿拉锡（Rashid Sidek）。  （图：大马国家体育理事会面子书）</figcaption></figure></li><li class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide"><figure><img loading="lazy" width="800" height="532" alt="" class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-24528" data-id="24528" src="https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/f7cf1bde-a07f-4255-99ba-f2986ed75a6d.jpg?x-oss-process=style/imgcompress" srcset="https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/f7cf1bde-a07f-4255-99ba-f2986ed75a6d.jpg?x-oss-process=style/imgcompress 800w, https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/f7cf1bde-a07f-4255-99ba-f2986ed75a6d-300x200.jpg 300w, https://atvoss.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/f7cf1bde-a07f-4255-99ba-f2986ed75a6d-768x511.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><figcaption class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption">謝儮好是大马史上首名残奥会羽毛球金牌得主！（图：大马国家体育理事会面子书）</figcaption></figure></li></ul><a class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-prev swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white" role="button"></a><a class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-next swiper-button-next swiper-button-white" role="button"></a><a aria-label="Pause Slideshow" class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-pause" role="button"></a><div class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_pagination swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-white"></div></div></div>



<p>羽毛球名将谢儮好（Cheah Liek Hou）今天下午（9月4日）在SU5级（上肢残障）决赛，直落两局力挫印尼“死敌”德瓦（Dheva Anrimusthi），为大马代表团赢得本届东京残奥会第二金！</p>



<p>羽毛球在东京残奥会首次被列入赛项。33岁的六届世界冠军谢儮好耗时50分钟，以21比17、21比15击败印尼世界一哥德瓦，不负众望地为大马史上首名残奥会羽球金牌得主！</p>



<p>世界排名第二的谢儮好自2019年10月开始累积国际赛35连胜，同时豪夺七连冠。此役后，他将与德瓦的交手纪录提升为4胜5负，其中近3次在决赛对战都是赢家，就包括去年二月的巴西残疾人羽毛球国际赛和今年四月的迪拜残疾人羽毛球国际赛。</p>



<p>在铜牌战中，世界排名第三的苏约以21比16、21比9轻取台湾的方振宇，让印尼带走银牌和铜牌。</p>



<p>在今早的半决赛，谢儮好以15比21、21比10、21比16逆转方振宇；世界排名第一的德瓦则以21比13、21比15在印尼内战中淘汰队友苏约。</p>



<p>2020东京残奥会将于周日（9月5日）闭幕。大马代表团的目标是3金，至今已有2金2银斩获。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
