		<title>大马单日新增19,057   凯里乐观预测数区疫情将好转</title>
		<link>https://atvnewsonline.com/asean/24486/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[李毓琇]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 04 Sep 2021 07:47:26 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[马来西亚]]></category>
